thread.title: CIS Football: Receiver Tyrone Pierre leads Laval past Concordia 42-27
thread.title_full: CIS Football: Receiver Tyrone Pierre leads Laval past Concordia 42-27 - Winnipeg Free Press

author: The Canadian Press
title: CIS Football: Receiver Tyrone Pierre leads Laval past Concordia 42-27
text:
QUEBEC CITY, Que. - Tyrone Pierre caught two touchdowns and totalled 311 receiving yards to lead the Laval Rouge et Or to a 42-27 win over the Concordia Stingers on Sunday in Canadian university football action.
Pierre averaged 28.3 yards per catch as Laval (5-0) continues to dominate the RSEQ division.
Quarterback Marc-Antoine Langevin completed 28-of-34 passes for 402 yards and two TDs. Hugo Richard made 5-of-6 passes for 80 yards and a touchdown.
Trenton Miller led Concordia (2-3) with 400 passing yards on 27-of-43 completions. He threw two TDs and an interception.
